sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ISVCPod as InferenceService Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>mTLS (optional)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-monitoring)
    participant Envoy as Istio Envoy Sidecar<br/>15020/TCP HTTP
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller
    participant ISVCMount as InferenceService Pod<br/>(Secret Mount)

    %% Flow 1: External Client Request to InferenceService (KServe Mode)
    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: External Client Request (KServe Mode)
    Client->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Router->>IstioGW: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080
    IstioGW->>ISVCPod: Inference request<br/>HTTP/8080 (mTLS optional)<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
    ISVCPod->>S3: Load model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS Signature v4
    S3-->>ISVCPod: Model artifacts
    ISVCPod-->>IstioGW: Prediction result
    IstioGW-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: JSON response

    %% Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Note over Prom,Envoy: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>ISVCPod: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    ISVCPod-->>Prom: Metrics (Prometheus format)
    Prom->>Envoy: Scrape Istio metrics<br/>HTTP/15020<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    Envoy-->>Prom: Envoy metrics

    %% Flow 3: Storage Secret Aggregation
    Note over Dashboard,ISVCMount: Flow 3: Storage Secret Aggregation
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.3<br/>Bearer Token<br/>Labels: opendatahub.io/managed=true
    K8sAPI-->>Dashboard: Secret created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Secrets (labeled)<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.3<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Secret change event

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.3<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>(Aggregated S3 credentials)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: storage-config updated

    ISVCMount->>K8sAPI: Mount storage-config Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.3<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ISVCMount: Secret data (S3 credentials)
